column5: brought tears to my eyes. congratulations sweetheart, you’re going to be fantastic parents
you’re stunning. that winged liner is fantastic

oh hell yeah. i’m actually a model and i’ve had days where i feel hot as fuck getting ready for a shoot, then cancelled because i feel like i look like the bottom of a hot garbage can. you gotta try to ignore those thoughts though. you’re beautiful just the way you are.. it’s a matter of reminding yourself and not letting bpd win
